name: Delta Donatello
desc: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle Donatello, but dressed up as a special forces soldier.  Comes with a tiny assault rifle.  Seems good for kids.

name: Michaelangelo
desc: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle Michaelangelo.  Classic style with no embellishments.

name: Military Leonardo
desc: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle Leonardo after joining the military.

name: Skateboarding Michaelangelo
desc: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle Michaelangelo with a skateboard, and a bright 90s kid outfit.  I would buy this one.

name: Super Donnie
desc: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle Donatello dressed up like batman for some reason.

name: Leonardo
desc: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle Leonardo, but in a new action figure style.  Not as good as the classic one.

name: Touchdown Tossin Leonardo
desc: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle Leonardo, dressed up in a football uniform.  Comes with a football and helmet.
